1
00:00:55,000 --> 00:01:00,000
The Story of Minglan

2
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:02,580
Episode 53

3
00:02:08,640 --> 00:02:09,640
You're awake.

4
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:09,840
Why are you sleeping here?

5
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:16,120
Since like you don't

6
00:03:16,120 --> 00:03:17,520
want me to sleep here.

7
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:21,960
No, you should get up now.

8
00:03:27,600 --> 00:03:30,960
It isn't daybreak yet.

9
00:03:31,920 --> 00:03:33,120
Let's sleep a little while more.

10
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,240
Regarding I...

11
00:03:50,880 --> 00:03:51,960
taking in a concubine,

12
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:53,560
if you feel upset

13
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:54,880
about it,

14
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:56,760
just tell me.

15
00:03:58,920 --> 00:04:00,440
It's nothing, really.

16
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:11,400
When I just entered your house

17
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:13,960
I didn't know your difficulties yet,

18
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:16,880
and I still didn't fully know

19
00:04:16,880 --> 00:04:18,320
the situation of your house.

20
00:04:19,440 --> 00:04:20,525
I was afraid that if there are too many people,

21
00:04:20,525 --> 00:04:21,360
it wouldn't be easy to control them.

22
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:24,720
Now,

23
00:04:26,400 --> 00:04:27,720
I already know

24
00:04:28,280 --> 00:04:29,880
the situation of this house.

25
00:04:32,400 --> 00:04:33,960
Your paternal aunt directly told it to me,

26
00:04:33,960 --> 00:04:34,525
and the eyes of the one

27
00:04:34,525 --> 00:04:35,360
from the adjacent house is watching.

28
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:36,840
I can't make a mistake.

29
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:38,920
In anyway,

30
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:40,080
I know that you love me dearly.

31
00:04:40,520 --> 00:04:42,200
You also had me manage the house, hence,

32
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:44,760
I must keep an eye of that Fengxian.

33
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:47,480
Once the situation is better,

34
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:48,600
I'll just drive her away.

35
00:04:52,400 --> 00:04:53,320
How come I can't feel you

36
00:04:53,320 --> 00:04:54,520
being jealous at all?

37
00:04:56,440 --> 00:04:57,800
I'm not jealous.

38
00:04:58,960 --> 00:05:00,760
Isn't that a good thing?

39
00:05:04,880 --> 00:05:05,480
No.

40
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:07,040
I'm getting up.

41
00:05:33,240 --> 00:05:35,120
The supervisor of the garden told me

42
00:05:35,840 --> 00:05:37,360
that in 10 to 15 days,

43
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:38,480
the work in the garden will be over.

44
00:05:41,160 --> 00:05:42,400
After counting it,

45
00:05:43,875 --> 00:05:45,115
the work has been dragged for 2 months.

46
00:05:46,325 --> 00:05:47,565
If we drag it longer,

47
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:49,720
I'm afraid that outsiders will start to talk.

48
00:05:51,500 --> 00:05:53,450
I'm thinking...

49
00:05:54,400 --> 00:05:56,520
Once the work in the garden is done,

50
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:58,800
let's open the manor and set up a banquet.

51
00:06:00,400 --> 00:06:01,480
And that will solve it.

52
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:04,960
You are the Big Madam of this house.

53
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:06,480
You have the final say.

54
00:06:08,480 --> 00:06:09,720
That would be a big banquet.

55
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:11,800
All our close friends and families will come.

56
00:06:12,280 --> 00:06:14,240
Marquis, you must make some time

57
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:15,360
to stay here and meet the guests.

58
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:19,120
Once you give out the news,

59
00:06:19,520 --> 00:06:21,160
people will already come to visit our house.

60
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:22,160
Visit our house?

61
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:23,160
Yes.

62
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:26,925
Those who are unable to come

63
00:06:26,925 --> 00:06:28,240
during that day,

64
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:29,640
who don't want to come,

65
00:06:30,520 --> 00:06:31,475
or afraid that coming will invite

66
00:06:31,475 --> 00:06:32,000
too much attention

67
00:06:32,280 --> 00:06:33,880
would come here to visit you

68
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:35,600
before the banquet.

69
00:06:37,080 --> 00:06:38,120
That early?

70
00:06:41,440 --> 00:06:42,800
If it's a hot furnace,

71
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:45,200
even if it's the sixth month of the year,

72
00:06:45,640 --> 00:06:47,120
someone would still rush here to get burned.

73
00:06:55,880 --> 00:06:57,360
You are indeed wise.

74
00:06:58,440 --> 00:06:59,440
I'm afraid that...

75
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:02,080
I'm afraid that the fire might get too strong,

76
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:04,160
and cause the furnace will collapse.

77
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:09,840
Indeed.

78
00:07:10,840 --> 00:07:12,720
Hence, you must guard this furnace well.

79
00:07:13,520 --> 00:07:15,480
You can't just let anyone put in a fire wood.

80
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:20,360
War is an extension of the government.

81
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:21,375
A banquet about merging of houses

82
00:07:21,375 --> 00:07:22,360
is also an extension of the government.

83
00:07:23,280 --> 00:07:24,280
You must be more careful.

84
00:07:24,440 --> 00:07:26,320
You must be more careful.

85
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:31,680
Now,

86
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:34,200
we are in one furnace.

87
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:38,000
Let's both be careful.

88
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:42,000
You decide about the merging banquet.

89
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:43,800
You must be careful

90
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:45,080
with those people from the adjacent manor.

91
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:47,360
I know.

92
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:53,480
My parents were not benevolent when I was little.

93
00:07:54,440 --> 00:07:55,680
You know this.

94
00:08:02,880 --> 00:08:04,160
Although my father

95
00:08:04,160 --> 00:08:05,040
was harsh on me,

96
00:08:06,280 --> 00:08:07,480
no matter he loved

97
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:09,400
or hated me,

98
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:10,840
they were real feelings.

99
00:08:12,640 --> 00:08:13,800
Unlike that stepmother of mine

100
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:14,920
who was just putting on a mask.

101
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:19,080
But how come I'm not as fierce to my stepmother

102
00:08:19,080 --> 00:08:19,680
compared to

103
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:21,480
how I treated my father?

104
00:08:23,200 --> 00:08:24,400
Do you know why?

105
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:27,040
Because stepmother is an outsider.

106
00:08:28,400 --> 00:08:29,280
Indeed.

107
00:08:31,640 --> 00:08:32,480
My father remarried

108
00:08:32,480 --> 00:08:34,120
and had my stepmother.

109
00:08:34,960 --> 00:08:36,720
When she had her own child,

110
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:38,200
I became an eyesore to her.

111
00:08:38,880 --> 00:08:40,280
I'm affecting their future,

112
00:08:40,280 --> 00:08:41,960
hence, she wishes that I die soon.

113
00:08:42,640 --> 00:08:43,760
She's so hateful,

114
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:45,280
but since I know

115
00:08:45,280 --> 00:08:46,200
that she's an outsider,

116
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:48,920
I didn't feel

117
00:08:48,920 --> 00:08:49,800
that much pain.

118
00:08:52,920 --> 00:08:53,880
But the old marquis

119
00:08:53,880 --> 00:08:55,160
is your biological father.

120
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:01,440
Yes.

121
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:04,880
Since I was little,

122
00:09:05,280 --> 00:09:07,200
my father was my sky.

123
00:09:09,280 --> 00:09:10,520
He was like a sky deity.

124
00:09:11,520 --> 00:09:13,640
I respected and loved him.

125
00:09:15,160 --> 00:09:16,520
No matter how he treated me,

126
00:09:16,520 --> 00:09:18,240
I'd always bear some hope towards him.

127
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:21,200
I felt that one day,

128
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:23,760
he would understand me.

129
00:09:25,040 --> 00:09:26,320
But until the end,

130
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:28,240
when my hope

131
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:29,560
completely shattered,

132
00:09:30,800 --> 00:09:32,320
I felt so much pain,

133
00:09:38,360 --> 00:09:39,080
because I feel

134
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:40,680
that he naturally should love me.

135
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:47,920
I understand.

136
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:51,600
You don't.

137
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:56,320
You are my wife.

138
00:09:57,480 --> 00:09:58,440
I understand.

139
00:09:59,800 --> 00:10:00,960
Although I treat you like the earth

140
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:03,000
looking up into the sky,

141
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:04,160
a star looking at that moon,

142
00:10:04,520 --> 00:10:07,080
I respect and love you.

143
00:10:11,640 --> 00:10:12,680
Let's just eat.

144
00:10:17,960 --> 00:10:18,920
Did I say something wrong?

145
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:22,240
You still don't get it!

146
00:10:34,400 --> 00:10:35,240
Shitou!

147
00:10:35,560 --> 00:10:35,825
Marquis!

148
00:10:35,825 --> 00:10:37,080
You're going to the morning court this early?

149
00:10:37,080 --> 00:10:38,160
Early? It's already late!

150
00:10:46,040 --> 00:10:47,360
What's wrong with Marquis?

151
00:10:47,360 --> 00:10:48,840
He seems unhappy?

152
00:10:50,760 --> 00:10:52,360
He has been weird since yesterday.

153
00:10:53,520 --> 00:10:55,160
Maybe, there are so many things

154
00:10:55,160 --> 00:10:56,360
to worry in the imperial court.

155
00:10:58,880 --> 00:11:00,280
Shitou brought you some food again?

156
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:02,480
Fried cherries from Nanbei Shop.

157
00:11:02,480 --> 00:11:03,400
Big Madam, have a taste.

158
00:11:09,520 --> 00:11:10,560
This is from Nanbei Shop?

159
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:12,000
Yes.

160
00:11:14,800 --> 00:11:15,600
Not bad.

161
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:17,800
The ones from Nanbei Shop are delicious.

162
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:19,200
That's right!

163
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:22,000
The work in the garden would be over soon.

164
00:11:22,680 --> 00:11:23,450
We would be setting up a banquet

165
00:11:23,450 --> 00:11:24,040
to entertain some guests.

166
00:11:24,640 --> 00:11:25,600
This desert is nice.

167
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:27,280
Tell the Desert Section to buy some

168
00:11:27,280 --> 00:11:28,400
and set it up during that day.

169
00:11:28,400 --> 00:11:29,680
Okay! Okay!

170
00:11:30,720 --> 00:11:31,480
That flaky crab apple flower

171
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:32,680
last time was good too.

172
00:11:32,680 --> 00:11:33,600
Add that too.

173
00:11:34,360 --> 00:11:35,240
That's right! That's right!

174
00:11:45,480 --> 00:11:46,280
Yancao! Yancao!

175
00:11:46,280 --> 00:11:46,825
Quickly come here.

176
00:11:46,825 --> 00:11:47,760
There are a lot of people today!

177
00:11:49,280 --> 00:11:50,840
Serve these dishes to the front.

178
00:11:50,840 --> 00:11:52,040
Danju!

179
00:12:01,220 --> 00:12:02,540
Put them according to kind.

180
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:03,840
Sister-in-law, slowly.

181
00:12:04,560 --> 00:12:05,360
Come. Come.

182
00:12:07,480 --> 00:12:08,760
Good rascal.

183
00:12:08,760 --> 00:12:10,560
Merging these two mansions

184
00:12:10,560 --> 00:12:11,760
really made it so huge.

185
00:12:12,680 --> 00:12:13,800
What's the use of being huge?

186
00:12:14,080 --> 00:12:15,960
Good thing, we just renovated the garden.

187
00:12:15,960 --> 00:12:17,520
Sister-in-law, take a good look at it.

188
00:12:17,760 --> 00:12:19,040
Crude men like us

189
00:12:19,040 --> 00:12:20,320
don't really know refined things.

190
00:12:20,880 --> 00:12:21,640
Sister-in-law,

191
00:12:21,640 --> 00:12:22,640
look and tell me

192
00:12:22,640 --> 00:12:23,680
if there are anything you don't like.

193
00:12:23,680 --> 00:12:25,200
The mason hasn't left yet.

194
00:12:25,200 --> 00:12:26,560
Marquis, you're being too courteous.

195
00:12:26,560 --> 00:12:27,640
Was it your wife

196
00:12:27,640 --> 00:12:28,640
who handled all the renovations?

197
00:12:29,840 --> 00:12:31,080
She did them all.

198
00:12:31,080 --> 00:12:32,320
What do I know?

199
00:12:33,920 --> 00:12:34,920
Come. Come.

200
00:12:35,440 --> 00:12:36,800
Make way!

201
00:12:38,360 --> 00:12:39,360
Please look at where you're going!

202
00:12:40,120 --> 00:12:41,200
A carriage from your manor.

203
00:13:09,360 --> 00:13:10,680
Husband, greetings!

204
00:13:13,640 --> 00:13:14,560
This one must be

205
00:13:14,560 --> 00:13:15,150
the Marquis Gu that older sister

206
00:13:15,150 --> 00:13:15,560
frequently mentioned

207
00:13:15,560 --> 00:13:17,240
when she was still alive. Am I right?

208
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:19,960
Greetings, Marquis.

209
00:13:20,240 --> 00:13:22,280
Congratulations on the merging of your houses!

210
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:26,150
This is the Third Little Sister

211
00:13:26,150 --> 00:13:26,800
of my deceased wife.

212
00:13:26,800 --> 00:13:28,800
She got taken in as my concubine a few days ago.

213
00:13:30,200 --> 00:13:31,325
Since General already

214
00:13:31,325 --> 00:13:32,800
has a concubine to serve you,

215
00:13:33,000 --> 00:13:34,800
forgive me for going home to rest then.

216
00:13:35,320 --> 00:13:37,400
Sister-in-law, don't.

217
00:13:38,360 --> 00:13:40,640
Sister, just feel free to go back.

218
00:13:40,720 --> 00:13:42,920
I surely will attend to husband well.

219
00:13:44,400 --> 00:13:46,040
You really want me to go back,

220
00:13:46,240 --> 00:13:47,600
but why must I leave?

221
00:13:47,920 --> 00:13:49,320
I'm not the one who's embarrassing myself here.

222
00:13:50,680 --> 00:13:51,280
Sister,

223
00:13:51,280 --> 00:13:52,680
don't blame husband for this.

224
00:13:52,760 --> 00:13:54,320
It was me who

225
00:13:54,320 --> 00:13:55,080
insisted on coming after seeing the invitation.

226
00:13:55,080 --> 00:13:55,720
Wife!

227
00:14:04,680 --> 00:14:05,800
What's going on here?

228
00:14:06,200 --> 00:14:08,240
You're slapping the face of the Zhang family here.

229
00:14:10,120 --> 00:14:11,400
In an official banquet,

230
00:14:11,400 --> 00:14:12,840
you've brought a concubine?

231
00:14:13,160 --> 00:14:14,560
This is against etiquette.

232
00:14:21,560 --> 00:14:22,275
Fifth was afraid that

233
00:14:22,275 --> 00:14:23,320
her pregnancy might get unstable,

234
00:14:23,320 --> 00:14:24,960
hence, she especially asked me to apologize to you

235
00:14:24,960 --> 00:14:26,120
for she can't come anymore.

236
00:14:26,960 --> 00:14:28,320
And Changbai

237
00:14:28,800 --> 00:14:29,280
went to attend to his duties

238
00:14:29,280 --> 00:14:30,800
in Hanlin Academy.

239
00:14:32,400 --> 00:14:34,400
He said that your husband knows that

240
00:14:34,400 --> 00:14:35,920
he doesn't like events like this,

241
00:14:36,160 --> 00:14:36,850
hence, he especially didn't

242
00:14:36,850 --> 00:14:37,440
send him any invitation.

243
00:14:37,600 --> 00:14:38,760
Really so considerate.

244
00:14:39,200 --> 00:14:40,160
When they get together,

245
00:14:40,160 --> 00:14:41,600
they would have endless talks.

246
00:14:41,600 --> 00:14:42,320
Yes.

247
00:14:43,280 --> 00:14:44,360
Congratulations. Congratulations.

248
00:14:45,280 --> 00:14:45,920
Thanks.

249
00:14:49,360 --> 00:14:51,360
How come you invited her too?

250
00:14:53,080 --> 00:14:54,360
There were originally two invitations.

251
00:14:54,560 --> 00:14:56,720
One is for Countess Wu.

252
00:14:57,050 --> 00:14:58,330
The one is for Fourth Brother-in-law.

253
00:14:59,360 --> 00:15:00,640
But when my messenger arrived in their manor,

254
00:15:00,680 --> 00:15:03,800
they said that Fourth Brother-in-law

255
00:15:04,160 --> 00:15:04,750
accompanied Countess Wu

256
00:15:04,750 --> 00:15:05,520
to Luzhou to buy paintings.

257
00:15:05,520 --> 00:15:07,280
The invitations then didn't reach them.

258
00:15:09,000 --> 00:15:10,760
I'm sure you calculated the days well

259
00:15:10,760 --> 00:15:11,840
before sending the invitations.

260
00:15:12,760 --> 00:15:13,840
A few days ago,

261
00:15:14,440 --> 00:15:15,675
my marquis husband especially

262
00:15:15,675 --> 00:15:16,840
told Fourth Brother-in-law

263
00:15:16,960 --> 00:15:18,400
that the painting that Countess Wu wants

264
00:15:18,680 --> 00:15:19,360
is in Luzhou.

265
00:15:20,240 --> 00:15:21,760
You husband and wife

266
00:15:22,240 --> 00:15:23,520
did it deliberately.

267
00:15:24,320 --> 00:15:25,400
But the next day,

268
00:15:25,840 --> 00:15:28,000
my mother-in-law sent an invitation

269
00:15:28,080 --> 00:15:30,000
to that Fourth Sister of mine.

270
00:15:31,240 --> 00:15:32,560
Your mother-in-law

271
00:15:33,080 --> 00:15:34,560
is quite famous.

272
00:15:34,760 --> 00:15:35,800
She's quite powerful

273
00:15:35,800 --> 00:15:37,200
among the wives of nobility.

274
00:15:38,240 --> 00:15:38,800
I remember that

275
00:15:38,800 --> 00:15:40,320
when Count Yan's house did a separation of assets,

276
00:15:40,600 --> 00:15:42,600
she was even especially invited to be a judge.

277
00:15:42,920 --> 00:15:44,280
Good thing, she's only a stepmother.

278
00:15:44,560 --> 00:15:45,800
Or else, your days

279
00:15:45,800 --> 00:15:47,320
would be harder than mine.

280
00:15:52,680 --> 00:15:53,240
Yes.

281
00:15:53,240 --> 00:15:55,120
If not, their family wouldn't have any decision

282
00:15:55,120 --> 00:15:57,000
on this asset separation matter.

283
00:15:57,000 --> 00:15:58,043
No such thing.

284
00:15:58,043 --> 00:15:59,440
I'm not that resolute.

285
00:16:01,800 --> 00:16:03,520
Since the Kang Family entered the capital,

286
00:16:03,760 --> 00:16:04,920
I had to return home every 3 to 5 days,

287
00:16:04,920 --> 00:16:05,680
Once I came home

288
00:16:06,120 --> 00:16:07,640
